      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63686436.pdf_57_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "叶底 软亮匀齐",
        "bbox": [
          0.678117998506348,
          0.41199294532627867,
          0.7617625093353249,
          0.46984126984126984
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63686436.pdf_57_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "紧结壮实，稍扭曲，色泽 油润",
        "bbox": [
          0.1423948220064725,
          0.44938271604938274,
          0.35847647498132934,
          0.4874779541446208
        ],
        "order": 9
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63686436.pdf_57_8",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "汤色深橙黄，香气浓长， 滋味醇厚，岩韵明显",
        "bbox": [
          0.42419716206123975,
          0.44938271604938274,
          0.6293253671894449,
          0.4888888888888889
        ],
        "order": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63686436.pdf_57_15",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "强心解挛：红袍中的咖啡碱具有强心、解痉、 松弛平滑肌的功效，能解除管痉挛，促进 血液循环。",
        "bbox": [
          0.5187951207368683,
          0.562962962962963,
          0.9131192432163306,
          0.6222222222222222
        ],
        "order": 13
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63686436.pdf_57_16",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "抗菌抑菌：红袍中的茶多酚和鞣酸作于细 菌，能凝固细菌的蛋白质，将细菌杀死。",
        "bbox": [
          0.5187951207368683,
          0.6335097001763669,
          0.9141150112023898,
          0.6730158730158731
        ],
        "order": 15
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63686436.pdf_57_17",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "最佳品饮时节春夏时节。",
        "bbox": [
          0.5267612646253423,
          0.691358024691358,
          0.7657455812795618,
          0.7118165784832452
        ],
        "order": 16
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63686436.pdf_57_19",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "红袍保存时最好不要使玻璃罐、瓷罐、 盒或药罐，因为这些器具具有透光、不防潮、 易碎的缺点。最好先用小罐子分装少量茶叶， 以便随时取用，其余的茶叶则大罐子密封起 来储存在冰箱里保存。",
        "bbox": [
          0.5187951207368683,
          0.76331569664903,
          0.9151107791884491,
          0.8641975308641975
        ],
        "order": 18
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63686436.pdf_57_13",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "武夷岩茶历史悠久，红袍乃是武夷岩茶中 的佼佼者。红袍之所以特别引关注，先 在于它的稀贵。历史上的大红袍，本来就少， 如今公认的红袍茶树，仅是九龙窠岩壁上 的那几棵。",
        "bbox": [
          0.08563604680109535,
          0.8105820105820106,
          0.48493900921085387,
          0.9107583774250441
        ],
        "order": 20
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-63686436.pdf_57_21",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "般群皆可饮，童、孕妇不适宜饮。",
        "bbox": [
          0.5197908887229276,
          0.9178130511463845,
          0.8882250435648494,
          0.9361552028218695
        ],
        "order": 22
      }
    ]
  },
